  "description": "<i>Spooks</i> is an action-adventure game where the goal is to collect eight musical\nboxes and play them at the exit. The game is set in and around \na large mansion which is haunted by four ghosts against which \nyou can defend by throwing large or heavy objects at. \nAround the mansion there are many rooms and many items whose \nfunction you need to figure out in order to complete the game.\nAdding to the suspense is the need to be on alert for the ghosts\nas they move quite fast and also that when in inventory menu\nyou only get a short time to make your decisions.\n",
